{
  "stem": "7282.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we used to-- they used to give us, like-- we used to work-- the, the system was the-- like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't work for an hour and getting hourly wages or daily wages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there, you worked [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a day about-- a day work, what you are doing it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Shall we say, you worked this part-- this type of work is worth, shall we say, a kilogram of, of flour, shall we say.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If you made some more over this, you got doubled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you had two kilograms of flour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was other types, this already-- it's-- when it started in the spring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It comes spring.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's farmed up already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was altogether different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then you got to go out, at that time, on the fields to, to make the fields, to-- I mean, how-- how to-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH]. in the field and [YIDDISH]-- ready the fields, to 'zeyen,' zeyen--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To sow-- to plant, to-- to Yeah. --plant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or what.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then it was different jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, like, it was a tractor, a company of tractors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have-- you got to ready the tractor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You got to plough the, the soil and to sow the grain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This type of work paid a lot more because it was heavier and it was demanding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I learned to, to operate a tractor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked on the tractor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So instead to get, shall we say, a kilo or two kilos, I had 40 pounds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had 10 kilos worth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if you was to work overtime, you used to get double worth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had flour.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, not flour, but grains-- they used to pay us not with money.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
